What is BILE?
=============
BILE is a command-line based, template-driven tool for generating static HTML 
content.


Basic usage
===========

bile [-f] [-v] [-l log file] [-s script file] -i input -o output -t template

-f: Force all output to be rebuilt irrespective of modification date
-i: Directory where input files are located
-l: Log file
-o: Directory where output files are written
-s: Script file for upload via FTP
-t: Directory where template files are located
-v: Verbose mode


